text: Nikolay Kuznetsov (, 1882 – after 1912) was a Russian fencer. He competed in the individual and team sabre events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1882 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
